Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.85,0:24:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs50}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你真觉得一个小不点孩子能当坏蛋吗\N{\fs50}You seriously think a puny little child can be a villain .
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 当然了 我很卑鄙的\N{\fs50}Umm... Yes. I'm pretty despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.86,0:24:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,惹恼我的后果可严重了\N{\fs50}You don't want to cross me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能偷走上古玉盘\N{\fs50}Evil is for adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.07,0:25:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能大肆破坏的成年人才配得上"邪恶"二字\N{\fs50}who steal powerful ancient stones and wreak havoc,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.25,0:25:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种应该在学校学习的小鬼头还是省省吧\N{\fs50}and not fortubby little pups who should be at school learning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪凉快哪待着去\N{\fs50}taking a recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的 我停不下来\N{\fs50}Suck,I can' stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等你有了能打动我的事迹再来吧\N{\fs50}Come back when youve done something to impress me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs50}Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.52,0:25:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是翼人 极恶六天王的下一位成员\N{\fs50}I am Wingman,the next member of The Vicious 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.73,0:25:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 这飞行之力\N{\fs50}Behold,the power of fight,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.74,0:25:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 别闹了 我出手了\N{\fs50}All right,joke's over. Show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这人也太能飞了\N{\fs50}Woothis is a big balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.20,0:25:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对对 转向 就是这样\N{\fs50}Yeah,yeah,turn around that”s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,家人们 拉过来 把他拉过来\N{\fs50}Bring him in. Bring him in,boysl
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.02,0:26:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿走了玉盘\N{\fs50}He took the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.77,0:26:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住他\N{\fs50}Caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁大楼\N{\fs50}Lock down the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.58,0:26:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我..别看我 没什么好看的\N{\fs50}I did. nothing to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.00,0:26:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 看看 弗兰普顿重生 品味不镜\N{\fs50}Oh,look at you. Frampton Comes Alive! Nice choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.55,0:26:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我....\N{\fs50}I uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.14,0:26:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走你的\N{\fs50}Just keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 一个孩子吗\N{\fs50}Look at that. A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.40,0:26:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\fs50}Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.16,0:27:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在这干什么\N{\fs50}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.83,0:27:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 快上车\N{\fs50}Okay.Just get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.83,0:27:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-他往哪走了 -小小偷在那\N{\fs50}-Which way did he go? -There is that little thief
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,开门 送快递的\N{\fs50}Knock knock. Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个恶魔般的孩子在那\N{\fs50}The demon child!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.53,0:27:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,奥托 把玉盘带回基地\N{\fs50}Otto,take the stone back to the lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我来转移他们的注意力\N{\fs50}I'll distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:28:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别吧 这时候故障拜托给点力啊\N{\fs50}No,not now. Come on,come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.86,0:28:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 宝贝\N{\fs50}Yeah,baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.45,0:28:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我来处理\N{\fs50}I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.50,0:28:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能享受你的短暂余生\N{\fs50}Hope you enjoy the rest of your short life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.75,0:28:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托别故障了 快点 快点\N{\fs50}Please work. Come on,come on,come on
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.68,0:28:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我们找你算账吧 小屁孩\N{\fs50}We're coming for you,tiny manl
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.83,0:29:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都说一个孩子不可能成为真正的坏蛋\N{\fs50}They all said a kid wouldn't be a real villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.54,0:29:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这个孩子刚刚从坏蛋头子那偷走些东西\N{\fs50}We-he-ell... This kid just stole something from the worst villains in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.26,0:29:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等我把这个还给他们的时候 他们会说\N{\fs50}When I bring it back to them,they're going to say....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.97,0:29:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们犯了个大错误"\N{\fs50}"We have made aterrible mistake."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.64,0:29:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"请加入我们吧"\N{\fs50}"Please join Us."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.98,0:29:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"加入我们吧 格鲁" 我会说\N{\fs50}"Please Gru" and I will say....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.27,0:29:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我会成为极恶六天王的新成员\N{\fs50}Yes! I will be the newest member of The Vicious 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我需要奥托\N{\fs50}Now all I need is Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.19,0:29:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奥托在哪\N{\fs50}Where is Otto?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.82,0:29:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 什么"奥托等会就来" 他现在就得在这儿\N{\fs50}No,not "Otto le komay" He needs to come in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.33,0:29:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-奥托 -小老板\N{\fs50}-Ottol -Mini boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.96,0:29:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\fs50}There you are....
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.21,0:30:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你带回来了吗\N{\fs50}You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.55,0:30:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是.... 你是在拖我后腿吗\N{\fs50}Is this.... Are you pulling on my legs right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.89,0:30:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,奥托 玉盘去哪里了\N{\fs50}Otto,where's the Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.93,0:30:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.81,0:30:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,宠物石
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.80,0:31:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你是把我的未来换给别人了吗\N{\fs50}Did you just trade my future?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.01,0:31:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了个宠物石头\N{\fs50}For a pet rock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.89,0:31:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 我自己去\N{\fs50}Okay I'll go..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.31,0:31:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的生日派对在哪里\N{\fs50}Where was this birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,无语 无语死了\N{\fs50}This is unacceptable. Unacceptablel
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.48,0:31:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你们说过 你们还不能加入大组织\N{\fs50}I told you guys that you weren' ready forthe big leagues
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.19,0:31:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你还用行动证明了我是对的\N{\fs50}and you have proven me correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只会捣乱\N{\fs50}All you do is mess everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.91,0:32:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 搞什么\N{\fs50}Ugh! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.17,0:32:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈说的对\N{\fs50}My mom was right,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.50,0:32:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不属于这里 你们被解雇了\N{\fs50}You do not belong here. You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去找那玉盘\N{\fs50}I'm going to find that stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.26,0:32:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家的时候 希望你们都消失了\N{\fs50}When I get home,you all better be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.31,0:32:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 奥托 你那嘴别再叭叭了\N{\fs50}And Otto,close your yapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}BGM：Goodbye to Love by Carpenters
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.90,0:32:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,与爱道别\N{\fs50}I'll say goodbye to love
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.24,0:32:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人在乎我的生死\N{\fs50}No one ever cared if l should leave or die
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.62,0:32:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}一次又一次 爱的机会与我肩而过\N{\fs30}Time and time again the chance for love has passed me by
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文 别跟着我了 我没你们更好\N{\fs50}Kevin,no,I will be better off on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.29,0:32:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}我所知道的关于爱的一切就是没有爱如何生活\N{\fs30}And all I konw of love is how to live without it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.71,0:32:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}我就是找不到爱\N{\fs30}I just can't seem to find it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.76,0:33:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}所以我下定决心 我必须独自生活\N{\fs30}So l've made my mind up I must live my life alone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.56,0:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}虽然这并不容易我想我一直都知道\N{\fs30}And though it's not the easy way I guess I've always know
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.10,0:33:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}与爱道别\N{\fs30}I'd say goodbye to love
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.65,0:33:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}我的真心没有未来\N{\fs30}There are no tomorrows for this heart of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.70,0:33:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}时间肯定会抹去这些苦涩的回忆\N{\fs30}Surely time will lose these bitter memories
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.79,0:33:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}我会发现原来还有一个人可以相信\N{\fs30}And I'll find that there is someone to believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}为了我人生的值得而活\N{\fs30}And to live for something I could live for
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.04,0:33:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小老板\N{\fs50}Mini boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我还以为这样就能打动你们\N{\fs50}I'm sorry.I thought you'll be impressed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我能和贝莱·博顿聊聊吗\N{\fs50}Can I just speak to Belle Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.40,0:33:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,威酷魔王\N{\fs50}Wild Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然还活着\N{\fs50}You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.15,0:33:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 我最喜欢的坏蛋居然绑架了我误\N{\fs50}Wow,my favorite villain is also my kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.90,0:33:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不杀我 这事儿我能吹一辈子\N{\fs50}This could be a great opportunity if you don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.37,0:34:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 把玉盘给我\N{\fs50}Shut up and give me the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.12,0:34:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊对对对 玉盘\N{\fs50}Ahh. Yes. The stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.08,0:34:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的\N{\fs50}Here's the thing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.54,0:34:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这个故事说起来还挺有趣\N{\fs50}It's kind of a funny story.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.79,0:34:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快把玉盘给他\N{\fs50}Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.30,0:34:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,事态马上就要严重起来了\N{\fs50}It's all going to go South very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.97,0:34:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈是什么\N{\fs50}What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.57,0:34:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,玉盘到底在哪 小屁孩\N{\fs50}Where is it,boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.95,0:34:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有 不在我这儿\N{\fs50}I don't have it,I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.08,0:34:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你把它藏起来了\N{\fs50}I know you're hiding it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.62,0:34:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有 我保证 我用我的生命起誓\N{\fs50}I'm not,I'm not. I swear. Cross my heart and hope to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,死我也不会干这事儿\N{\fs50}Stick a needle in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.12,0:34:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我扔下去\N{\fs50}Don't actually do that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.62,0:34:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来人 把电话拿来\N{\fs50}Somebody bring me a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.30,0:34:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,打电话给家里人吧 勒索时间到了\N{\fs50}Call home. It's ransom time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.13,0:35:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别别别 我妈可能还会给你钱感谢你把我绑走\N{\fs50}No,no,no. My mom will probably pay you to keep me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.22,0:35:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别想耍我 快打\N{\fs50}Good one. Call
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.72,0:35:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊\N{\fs50}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.39,0:35:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文什么\N{\fs50}Kevin lay what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.85,0:35:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你逗我呢 小屁孩还有手下\N{\fs50}You kidding me? You got henchmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.35,0:35:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 我死定了\N{\fs50}Well,that's the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.44,0:35:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我听好 把玉盘带来旧金山\N{\fs50}Listen,you. Bring the stone to me in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.69,0:35:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,格林街6830号 听见没 给你两天时间\N{\fs50}6830 Green Street,got it? Now you got two days
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.03,0:36:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就别想再见到你的小老板了\N{\fs50}oryou are never gonna see your little boss again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.25,0:36:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 那玉盘子\N{\fs50}Oh ho ho... The stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.51,0:37:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给我叔叔啦 这东西比较适合他嘛\N{\fs50}Gave that to my uncle. It's more his style.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说了 我不知道他去哪了 笨蛋\N{\fs50}I told you,I don't know where he went you stupid Twinkies,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.34,0:37:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了\N{\fs50}Not cool man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.69,0:38:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去往旧金山之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,旧金山\N{\fs50}San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.04,0:38:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧 是时候把我们的玉盘拿回来了\N{\fs50}Let's rock and roll. Time to get our stone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.63,0:38:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,格鲁先生 我们来咯\N{\fs50}Were coming for you Mr. Gru,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.17,0:38:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利路亚\N{\fs50}Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.11,0:38:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,国际机场
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.67,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去旧金山 好的 您要怎么支付呢\N{\fs50}San Francisco. Okay. How will you be paying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.93,0:39:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你要再是支付个毛球我们就可以把你升去头等舱呢\N{\fs50}Oh great. You know,if you have any hairballs,we can upgrade you to 1st class.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.02,0:39:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚\N{\fs50}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不在拉瓜迪亚调头\N{\fs50}And I had to turn back at LaGuardi\N{\fs50}a.
