Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.58,0:40:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 宝宝 花生要吗\N{\fs50}Hey baby,Peanut?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看见我啦看不见啦\N{\fs50}You see me? You see me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.80,0:42:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,旧金山
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.53,0:42:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子有点东西 敢从极恶六天王手里偷东西\N{\fs50}You got real moxie kid,stealing from The Vicious 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.28,0:42:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有点东西 真的吗 这是威酷魔王对我的夸赞吗\N{\fs50}I got moxie,really? Did I just receive a compliment from Wild Knuckles?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.24,0:42:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,梦想成真啦\N{\fs50}All my dreams are coming true right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.87,0:42:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那梦想要变成噩梦咯\N{\fs50}Well it's about to become your nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎使用我最新的酷刑装置迪斯科地狱\N{\fs50}Welcome to my newest torture device. Disco inferno
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.80,0:42:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小黄人最好在明天太阳下山之前赶过来哦\N{\fs50}Your minions better get it by sundown tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.93,0:42:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果48小时的迪斯科折磨不死你 那你就要被锯死啦\N{\fs50}because if48 hours of disco won't kill you,the blade will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.10,0:42:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 不要啊\N{\fs50}Oooh! No,no,no,no,no,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.80,0:43:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}前方死亡谷 最好现在回头路\N三百里后有加油站
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.77,0:43:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走继续走\N{\fs50}Go go go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.23,0:43:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,格林街
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.35,0:44:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下一站 格林街\N{\fs50}Next up,Green Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.77,0:44:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an8}威\N酷\N威\N酷
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.30,0:45:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs50}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.72,0:45:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有入侵者\N{\fs50}Trespassers!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.69,0:45:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,给我回来\N{\fs50}Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.60,0:46:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别想跑 给我回来\N{\fs50}Get your little butts back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.68,0:46:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,周氏针灸
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.81,0:46:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你会感觉有点痛\N{\fs50}OK,now. You might feel a little pinch,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.70,0:46:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到你们了\N{\fs50}Got you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.95,0:46:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好戏开始\N{\fs50}Time to bring some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.09,0:46:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,周末有没有安排呀\N{\fs50}Any plans for the weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.93,0:46:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,做五个深呼吸\N{\fs50}Take five deep breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.89,0:46:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fs50}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.18,0:46:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们喜欢其负小孩子是吧\N{\fs50}You like picking on little guys,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.56,0:47:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,睡你的午觉去吧 老东西\N{\fs50}Go take a nap,old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢叫我老东西\N{\fs50}old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.91,0:47:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是少林功夫大师\N{\fs50}I am a master of the ancient Shaolin Art of Kung Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.36,0:47:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,回家找妈妈去吧\N{\fs50}Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.78,0:47:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要是再敢问进我们的地盘 必死无疑\N{\fs50}If you come backto our place,you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.25,0:48:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 要是真的想感谢我 就赶紧走 我工作呢\N{\fs50}Shh shh shh... You can thank me by going away. I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.26,0:48:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 想学功夫\N{\fs50}You? Want to learn Kung Fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.11,0:48:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不再收弟子了\N{\fs50}My teaching days are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.16,0:48:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想过平静的生活\N{\fs50}This is my life now,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.09,0:48:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs50}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.22,0:48:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是我徒弟了\N{\fs50}I will teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.06,0:49:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs50}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.69,0:49:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这些不是给你吃的\N{\fs50}those are not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的是给我卖 东西\N{\fs50}The name of the game is sell,sell,sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.73,0:49:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,特百惠派对
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.25,0:49:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fs50}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.22,0:49:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,格鲁在哪里\N{\fs50}Where is Gru?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.09,0:49:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道 你们这些花里胡哨的装扮是什么情况\N{\fs50}How should I know? What's with the costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.76,0:49:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,离万圣节还有好几个月呢 你们穿得傻不拉几和干什么\N{\fs50}Halloween was four months ago. You look stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.85,0:49:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\fs50}Buzz off. Shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.81,0:49:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的松肉粉快好了\N{\fs50}I'm getting my meat tenderizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.14,0:49:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 让我来帮你吧\N{\fs50}Let me help you with that,dearie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.11,0:49:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快告诉我 那小孩在哪儿\N{\fs50}Now,where's the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.36,0:49:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是有意要恐吓你们的\N{\fs50}I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.57,0:49:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我们没有生他的气\N{\fs50}Don't worry,we're not mad at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.45,0:49:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是想....\N{\fs50}We just want to....
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.62,0:50:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,招募他\N{\fs50}hire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西在哪里\N{\fs50}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.63,0:50:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,威酷魔王 他还活著\N{\fs50}Wild Knuckles? He's alive
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.75,0:50:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子跟他组队了\N{\fs50}And working with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.30,0:50:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下一站旧金山\N{\fs50}We're going to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.38,0:50:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs50}Let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.93,0:50:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们最好赔偿我的房顶\N{\fs50}You had better be paying for my roof .
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.98,0:50:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前一亮 对吧\N{\fs50}Pretty groovy,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.07,0:50:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,基本功
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.91,0:50:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从基本腿法练起\N{\fs50}We begin with a basic kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.95,0:50:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们试试看\N{\fs50}Now,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.08,0:50:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不练这个了\N{\fs50}Okay.... No kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.17,0:50:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫瓜锤 是一件兵器\N{\fs50}This is a melon hammer. It's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.88,0:50:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是弗莱德 他是个人形靶\N{\fs50}This is Fred. Heis a dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.71,0:50:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要低估一个人形靶\N{\fs50}Never underestimate a dummy,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.80,0:51:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出手 攻击\N{\fs50}Now,attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.62,0:51:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跟我说你们碎不了木板\N{\fs50}Don't tell to me "I can not break this wood."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.75,0:51:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,自我怀疑只是心理作用\N{\fs50}But doubt exists only in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.96,0:51:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道我会对自己说什么吗\N{\fs50}You know what I say to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.92,0:51:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到你们了\N{\fs50}Now,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.77,0:51:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凯文啊 凯文 唉\N{\fs50}Kevin,Kevin,Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.24,0:52:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 看来你们还没做好学哲学的准备\N{\fs50}Okay. Clearly,we are not ready for philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.96,0:52:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就光训练吧\N{\fs50}Let's just train.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.99,0:52:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好好休息 明天的课会更累\N{\fs50}Rest up. Tomorrow's going to be even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.75,0:52:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你们要辞职\N{\fs50}What? You're quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.09,0:52:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说了 等拿到了玉盘\N{\fs50}Itold you when I get that stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.59,0:52:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就能所向披靡\N{\fs50}We're going to be unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.92,0:53:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够了\N{\fs50}I have had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.67,0:53:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么比一个上了年纪的坏蛋更可悲的了\N{\fs50}There's nothing sadderthan an aging villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.09,0:53:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 臭老头\N{\fs50}So long,old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.18,0:53:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样各位 我们可是一个团队\N{\fs50}Guys,come on. We're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.73,0:53:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你会喜欢\N{\fs50}Hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.90,0:53:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是天堂吗\N{\fs50}Is this heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.70,0:53:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚开除了那群狗腿子 知道为什么吗\N{\fs50}I just had to fire my henchman. You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.41,0:53:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们失职了\N{\fs50}Because they weren't getting the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.20,0:53:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我现在要给你松绑 因为我\N{\fs50}OK I'm just gonna untie you now because I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.45,0:53:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我需要你为我做一些家务\N{\fs50}I I I need you to do some stuff for me around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.75,0:53:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你 你懂的 有个伴总好过孤身一人\N{\fs50}You might be,you know,kind of nice to have a little company around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.09,0:53:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 没错\N{\fs50}Oh,yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.63,0:53:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,坏蛋做家务\N{\fs50}Villains just doing some chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.38,0:53:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道我们会遇到什么糟心事呢\N{\fs50}Who knows what kind of trouble we could get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.93,0:53:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs50}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.76,0:53:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的邪恶坏笑吗 -显而易见\N{\fs50}-That's your evil chuckle? -Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.81,0:53:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,简直糟透了\N{\fs50}Well,it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.94,0:53:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来就像个误食了卡祖笛的小丑\N{\fs50}You sound like a clown who swallowed a kazo\N{\fs50}o.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.35,0:54:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 那你就像一个土埋半截的老巫师\N{\fs50}Really? Well,you look like a wizard going through an end of life crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}唐·里克斯:著名讽刺喜剧演员
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别太嚣张了 唐.里克斯\N{\fs50}Easy now,Don Rickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.53,0:54:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,唐·里克斯是谁\N{\fs50}Who's Don Rickles?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.36,0:54:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,响尾蛇出没
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.43,0:54:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小家伙\N{\fs50}Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.47,0:54:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点以为你要不行了\N{\fs50}I thought we lost youthere for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.81,0:54:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 别激动 别激动\N{\fs50}Hey,chill chill,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.44,0:54:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要这个是吗 小兄弟\N{\fs50}You wanna try this one,little dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.61,0:54:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好兄弟 你是要去哪里\N{\fs50}Hey soul brother where jetting off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.36,0:54:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,旧金山啊\N{\fs50}Frisco Disco!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是个幸运的小家伙 我正好要去沿海那一带\N{\fs50}It's so lucky day chickTm heading up the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.37,0:54:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以载你一程\N{\fs50}I could drop you off on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.22,0:55:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最大的香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.04,0:55:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,旧金山 75公里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.00,0:55:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,从泳池开始 要打扫得干干净稳\N{\fs50}Start with the pool. This place gotta be spick and span.,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.25,0:55:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要干什么\N{\fs50}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.34,0:55:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去就像我妈妈在感恩节烤过头的火鸡\N{\fs50}You look like the overcooked turkey my mom makes on Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.85,0:55:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对了 我忘了提\N{\fs50}Oh yeah,I forgot to mention,,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.43,0:55:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面都是我的宠物鳄鱼\N{\fs50}the pool is filled with my pet crocodiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.10,0:56:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊好啊 这吓不倒我\N{\fs50}Yeah,well well... doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.57,0:56:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 可别缺了条胳膊\N{\fs50}Be careful.I can't have you lose an arm
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.74,0:56:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,待会我还想让你换灯泡呢 给我\N{\fs50}because they need you to change some light bulbs after this,yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.70,0:56:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你演示一下\N{\fs50}Let me show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.99,0:56:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别咬\N{\fs50}Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.79,0:56:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 哦 不妙\N{\fs50}Hey. Whoa! Oh,no.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.50,0:56:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,马文 别这样 快停下\N{\fs50}Marvin,no,no. Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.47,0:56:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把网递给我\N{\fs50}The net.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.39,0:56:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我来救你\N{\fs50}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.35,0:56:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓住了 加把劲\N{\fs50}I got you.I got you,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.93,0:56:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我没救到\N{\fs50}I don't got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.81,0:56:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手\N{\fs50}Take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.69,0:56:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住你了\N{\fs50}Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.91,0:57:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以跑的 但你....但你却留下来救了我\N{\fs50}You could have ran. But you.... But you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.20,0:57:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过的 你是我在这个世界上最喜欢的坏蛋\N{\fs50}I told you,you were my favorite villain in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.21,0:57:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能让你被鳄鱼吃掉\N{\fs50}I could not let you get eaten by crocodiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.05,0:57:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,即使那场面可能看起来会很酷\N{\fs50}Even though that would have been kinda cool to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.26,0:57:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以.....你是想成为一个很历害的大坏蛋 对吗\N{\fs50}So Soyouwantto be a great villain,huh?
