Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.03,1:01:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快来个人救救他\N{\fs50}Somebody help him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.36,1:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快救救我爷爷\N{\fs50}My grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.33,1:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要命了不行了\N{\fs50}This is the big one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.08,1:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\fs50}You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.42,1:01:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是甜美的天使之声\N{\fs50}It's the sweet sound of angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.00,1:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我 我眼前开始走马灯了\N{\fs50}Do something,my life is flashing before my eyes.
