Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.48,1:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,干得还不错\N{\fs50}Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.78,1:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们合作得很棒\N{\fs50}We make a good team.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.44,1:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs50}We do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.74,1:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 嘿 我们得这样做下去\N{\fs50}Oh yeah,hey we got to keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.41,1:03:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看好接下来我要教你的东西\N{\fs50}Wait till you see what I'm gonna teach you next.
