Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.58,1:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信他们竟然这样对我\N{\fs50}I can't believe they did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.71,1:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我把我会的都教给了他们\N{\fs50}I…I taught them everything they know.
