Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.39,1:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,终于抓住你了\N{\fs50}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.68,1:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在牢里待很久 很久\N{\fs50}You are going awayfor along,long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.23,1:16:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我可不这么想\N{\fs50}Yeah,well I wouldn't bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.19,1:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs50}No.
